{"tid":2316074,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得今年經濟幾好，生活仲好過之前。","createTime":"2020-12-07T14:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T11:22:31.000Z","uid":365088,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17ce6551b31009e0012e76f76c3e0c20952596a2","tid":2316074,"uid":365088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"樓市不斷升<br />\n條街勁多人，痴撚線<br />\nDonki係咁開,壽司郎都係<br />\n身邊冇人比人炒<br />\n仲要加左人工<br />\n加人工都請唔到人,痴線<br />\n老老實實 你地身邊多唔多人失業<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2315519/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2315519/page/1</a><br />\n經濟差？邊撚度差呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2208426/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2208426/page/1</a><br />\n經濟差係邊?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1766979/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1766979/page/1</a><br />\n經濟差？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2012960/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2012960/page/1</a><br />\n香港好多人失業經濟又差<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2314232/page/7\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2314232/page/7</a><br />\n<br />\n痴線,估唔到今年個生活仲好過之前,唔移民了<br />\n香港生活得咁好,個樓市經濟氣氛咁都頂得住,點解仲要移民<br />\n其他國家差到咁，不了，香港咁既環境已經唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2816087/%E3%80%90BNO%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E3%80%91%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%A9%BA%E7%BC%BA%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C%20%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%9A%B4%E5%B3%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2816087%2F%25E3%2580%2590BNO%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B7%258C%2520%25E6%25AD%2590%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%259A%25B4%25E5%25B3%25BB&d=JQtp7%2BS